      • main

        public static final void main(java.lang.String[] arguments)
        Entry point.
        Parameters:
        arguments - Command-line arguments

        Usage: Undercamber [flag parameters]...

        Flag Parameter1 Parameter2 Parameter3 Parameter4 Description
        -a automatically run all tests
        -tag1 tagNames automatically run tests with specified tags
        -tag2 tagNames testSetNames automatically run tests with specified tag. Limit search for tags to specified testSets.
        -test1 className methodName automatically run specified test and subtests. No arguments.
        -test2 className methodName arguments automatically run specified test and subtests, with arguments.
        -test3 testSetList className methodName automatically run specified test and subtests. Limit search for test to specified testSets. No arguments.
        -test4 testSetList className methodName arguments automatically run specified test and subtests. Limit search for test to specified testSets. With arguments.
        -rootDirectory directoryName output root directory name
        -subdirectory name output subdirectory name, Default built from current time and date)
        -config className name of configuration class
        -threadCount threadCount concurrent thread count
        -p parameter parameter passed to test processes
        -pp parameter1 parameter2 parameter pair passed to test processes
        -g automatically run tests selected in the GUI (from previous run)
        -set testSetName automatically run all tests in the specified test set
        -resultWindow true or false show or hide the results screen
